<title>STANDING ON THE PROMISES</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Lalpen Krista thutiem haw a ding-in,
 Kumsawt chanin A chawihatna la gi hen;
 Chungnung penah lopina pak la sa'ng ka,
 Pathien thutiem haw achun ding-in.

[V2]
 Ding-in...... ding-in,
 Ka Hukdampa Pathien thutiem haw a ding-in;
 Ding-in...... ding-in,
 Pathien thutiem haw achun ka ding hi.

[V3]
 2. Thutiem det leh zuou ngeilo haw a ding-in,
 Ginlahna lauhna huihpi'n ei mut laiin;
 Pathien thuhing mangin ken zo zel ing ka,
 Pathien thutiem haw achun ding-in.

[V4]
 3. Thutiem haw chunga ding-in tun ka mu thei,
 Kei din thisana silthienna bukim chuh;
 Kristan suohchakna A siem achun ding-in,
 Pathien thutiem haw achun ding-in.

[V5]
 4. Ka Lalpa Krista thutiem haw a ding-in,
 Hehpihna guiin Amah tawh ei zawm hi;
 Thagau chemzam a nichenga gal do in,
 Pathien thutiem haw achun ding-in.

[V6]
 5. Thutiem haw achun ding-in puk ngei puo'ng ka,
 Thagau Thiengtho sapna hun chenga ngaitha'n;
 Bangkima ka Bangkim Lalpa a chawlin,
 Pathien thutiem haw achun ding-in.</lyrics>
</song>